<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="forbid-vt">forbid <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fə'bɪd/    美 /fər'bɪd/  </p>
<p>(forbade, forbidden)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-allow-permit">1.★ <strong>禁止【反:allow / permit】；妨碍；阻止：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The American government forbids the sales of any alcohol to those under age 21.
美国政府禁止向不满21岁的人售酒。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>forbid sb from doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father forbade me from meeting net friends.
父亲禁止我去见网友。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>forbid sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I will forbid you to leave unless you apologize for what you have done.
如果你不为自己所做的事情道歉，我不会让你离开。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 2</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>forbid (sb) doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The regulations forbid smoking in this room.
根据规定，此室内禁止吸烟。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>forbid sb sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My doctor has forbidden me sugar. 
医生禁止我吃糖。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>forbidden /fə'bɪdn/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>forbidden fruit</strong>
禁果</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Forbidden City 
紫禁城</p></div></div>